  <FLAVOURTEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="en-US"><![CDATA[It eats what it wants to eat—which is anything that moves.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="fr-FR"><![CDATA[Elle mange tout ce qu’elle veut — et elle veut tout ce qui bouge.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="es-ES"><![CDATA[Come lo que quiere comer, que es todo lo que se mueva.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="de-DE"><![CDATA[Es frisst, was es fressen will – also alles, was sich bewegt.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="it-IT"><![CDATA[Mangia tutto quel che vuole... che è tutto quel che si muove.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="jp-JA"><![CDATA[そいつは食いたいものを食う—動くものなら何でもだ。]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="ko-KR"><![CDATA[웜은 움직이는 것이라면 닥치는 대로 먹는다.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
